1925;;Cheaper to Marry;;American;;Robert Z. Leonard;;Conrad Nagel, Lewis Stone, Marguerite De La Motte;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cheaper_to_Marry;;Matrimony is not only a good thing, but also a good financial deal: Lawyer Dick Tyler (Conrad Nagel) makes his merger bid for artist Doris (Marguerite De La Motte) as his partner Jim Knight (Lewis Stone) squanders the firm's asset on gold-digger Evelyn (Paulette Duval).